blurt 1.0 ShowCategories.pm
===========================

A plugin for blurt 1.0 that displays a list of all categories
in your blog

By Matthijs de Jonge (rhmtts@gmail.com).

This software is public domain software: do with it whatever you want.


INSTALL:
========

- Upload ShowCategories.pm to the plugins directory of your blurt
  installation on the server

VARIABLES:
==========

The ShowCategories  plugin supplies the following variables for use in all
templates:

$ShowCategories::display   : a list (<ul>) of all categories in your site
